linalg.lsqr.html#scipy.sparse.linalg.lsqr" title=3D"(in SciPy v1.16.2)"><co=
de class=3D"xref py py-func docutils literal notranslate"><span class=3D"pr=
e">scipy.sparse.linalg.lsqr</span></code></a> when
fitting on sparse training data. This parameter has no effect when fitting
on dense data.</p>
<div class=3D"versionadded">
<p><span class=3D"versionmodified added">Added in version 1.7.</span></p>
